    <fr:title text="Restriction of path objects along quasi-inverses">Restriction of <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" title="Path object" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" type="local">path objects</fr:link> along <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" title="Quasi-inverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" type="local">quasi-inverses</fr:link></fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
    <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001S.agda" type="external">erct-001S.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" title="Path object" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" type="local">path object</fr:link> and let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> be a type. Given a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" title="Quasi-inverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000X/" type="local">quasi-inverse</fr:link> function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\colon  B\to  
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert \mathcal {A}\right \rvert \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex>, we can restrict the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" title="Path object" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" type="local">path object</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex> to a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" title="Path object" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0010/" type="local">path object</fr:link> structure <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g^*\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex> on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> as follows:</html:p><fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 \begin {aligned}
  
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert g^*\mathcal {A}\right \rvert \mathclose {}
 &:\equiv  B\\
  x \approx _{g^*\mathcal {A}} y &:\equiv  gx \approx _{\mathcal {A}} gy\\
  \mathsf {rx}_{g^*\mathcal {A}}x &:\equiv  \mathsf {rx}_{\mathcal {A}}
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen gx\right \rparen \mathclose {}

 \end {aligned}
]]></fr:tex>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x:B]]></fr:tex>, we must show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}gx\approx _{\mathcal {A}}gy]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" type="local">proposition</fr:link>. But this is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" type="local">retract</fr:link> of  <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}gx\approx _{\mathcal {A}}y]]></fr:tex>, which is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" type="local">proposition</fr:link> by the univalence of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex>; thus the result follows from the closure of <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" type="local">propositions</fr:link> under <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" title="Retract" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" type="local">retracts</fr:link> (<fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" title="propositions are closed under retracts" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" /></fr:link>).</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
